data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF INSTALLED 12/23!!! Come see this delightful 3BR, 2 BA brick home on a .31 acre corner lot with mature trees. Step inside to find a thoughtfully designed split floor plan that ensures both privacy and functionality. New LVP has been added to the main living area,  with new lighting, hardware and paint throughout the house. Your spacious master suite offers a private retreat with an en-suite bathroom. Outdoors, the charm continues with ample outdoor space, perfect for relaxation or gathering on the patio! Don't forget this is COUNTY TAXES, PUTTING MORE MONEY IN YOUR POCKET!! This home is located with a quick jump into town. Make this delightful house your forever home.
